quran[62]{c,v,t}:
  37,83,Ndithudi pakati pa iwo amene amatsatira njira yake adali Abrahamu
  37,84,Pamene iye adadza kwa Ambuye wake ndi mtima woyera
  37,85,"Pamene iye adati kwa atate wake ndi anthu a mtundu wake, “Kodi ndi chiyani chimene inu muli kupembedza?”"
  37,86,“Kodi mukufuna milungu yabodza kapena Mulungu weniweni?”
  37,87,“Kodi mukuganiza zotani za Ambuye wa zolengedwa zonse?”
  37,88,Ndipo iye adayang’ana nyenyezi
  37,89,"Ndipo iye adati, “Ndithudi ndili kudwala.”"
  37,90,Kotero iwo adamusiya ndi kubwerera
  37,91,"Ndipoiyeadayang’anakwamilunguyawonati, “Kodi inu simudya?”"
  37,92,“Kodi bwanji inu simuyankhula?”
  37,93,Ndipo iye adadza pafupi ndi iyo ndi kuigwetsa ndi dzanja lake lamanja
  37,94,Nthawi yomweyo wopembedza mafano adadza kwa iye mwamsangamsanga
  37,95,"Iye adati, “Kodi mumapembedza zinthu zimene inu mwasema?”"
  37,96,“Pamene Mulungu ndiye amene adakulengani inu pamodzi ndi zosemasema zanuzi!”
  37,97,"Iwo adati, “Mupangireni ng’anjo ndipo muponyeni m’moto woyaka!”"
  37,98,Iwo adachita chiwembu koma Ife tidawachititsa manyazi
  37,99,"Ndipo iye adati, “Ine ndithawira kwa Ambuye wanga. Ndipo Iye adzanditsogolera ine.”"
  37,100,“Ambuye wanga! Ndipatseni ana kuchokera kwa ochita ntchito zabwino.”
  37,101,Ndipo Ife tidamuuza nkhani yabwino ya mwana wamwamuna wopirira
  37,102,"Ndipo pamene iye adakula mofika pa msinkhu woti angathe kuthandiza abambo ake, iye adati: “Mwana wanga! Ndithudi ine ndalota ndili kukupha ngati nsembe. Taganiza zimene uli kuziona.” Iye adati, “Atate wanga! Inu chitani monga momwe mwalamulidwira. Ngati Mulungu afuna, mudzandipeza ine wopirira!”"
  37,103,"Ndipo pamene onse adadzipereka, ndipo adamugoneka iye chafufumimba"
  37,104,"Ndipo Ife tidamuitana ndipo tidati, “Iwe Abrahamu!”"
  37,105,“Ndithudi wakwaniritsa maloto ako.” Ndithudi mmenemo ndi mmene timaperekera mphotho kwa anthu ochita zabwino
  37,106,Ndithudi awa adali mayesero oonekeratu
  37,107,Ndipo tidamupatsa iye nsembe yaikulu
  37,108,Ndipo Ife tidakhazikitsa ulemu pa iye pakati pa mibadwo yamtsogolo
  37,109,Mtendere ukhale pa Abrahamu
  37,110,Mmenemo ndi mmene timalipira mphotho kwa anthu ochita zabwino
  37,111,Ndithudi iye adali mmodzi wa akapolo athu okhulupirira
  37,112,"Ndipo Ife tidamuuza nkhani yabwino ya Isake, Mtumwi, wochokera pakati pa anthu okhulupirira"
  37,113,Ndipo Ife tidaika madalitso athu pa iye ndi pa Isake. Ndipo pakati pa ana awo pali ena ochita ntchito zabwino ndi ena amene ndi olakwa ndipo amadzipondereza okha
  37,114,"Ndipo, ndithudi, Ife tidaonetsa chisomo chathu kwa Mose ndi Aroni"
  37,115,Ndipo tidawapulumutsa onse pamodzi ndi anthu awo ku mavuto oopsa
  37,116,Ndipo Ife tidawathandiza kotero adali opambana
  37,117,Ndipo Ife tidawapatsa Buku Lopatulika limene limathandiza kufotokoza zinthu momveka bwino
  37,118,Ndipo Ife tidawatsogolera ku njira yoyenera
  37,119,Ndipo Ife tidakhazikitsa ulemu kwa iwo pakati pa mibadwo ya mtsogolo
  37,120,“Mtendere ukhale pa Mose ndi Aroni.”
  37,121,Ndithudi mmenemo ndi mmene timaperekera mphotho kwa anthu ochita ntchito zabwino
  37,122,Ndithudi onse adali akapolo athu okhulupirira
  37,123,Ndithudi Eliya anali mmodzi wa Atumwi
  37,124,"Pamene, iye adati kwa anthu ake, “Kodi inu simungaope Mulungu?”"
  37,125,“Kodi muli kupembedza Bala ndi kusiya kupembedza Namalenga?”
  37,126,"“Mulungu, Ambuye wanu ndi Ambuye wa makolo anu akale?”"
  37,127,"Koma iwo adamukana iye ndipo ndithudi, iwo adzatengedwa"
  37,128,Kupatula akapolo osankhidwa a Mulungu
  37,129,Ndithudi tidakhazikitsa ulemu kwa iye pakati pa mibadwo ya patsogolo
  37,130,“Mtendere ukhale ndi Eliya.”
  37,131,Ndithudi mmenemo ndi mmene timaperekera mphotho kwa anthu ochita ntchito zabwino
  37,132,Ndithudi iye adali mmodzi wa akopolo athu okhulupirira
  37,133,Ndipo Loti adali mmodzi wa Atumwi
  37,134,"Pamene, Ife tidamupulumutsa iye pamodzi ndi onse omutsatira"
  37,135,Kupatula mayi mmodzi wokalamba amene adali m’gulu la anthu otsalira m’mbuyo
  37,136,Ndipo Ife tidawaononga onse
  37,137,Ndithudi inu mumawadutsa nthawi ya m’mawa
  37,138,"Ndi nthawi yausiku, kodi inu simungazindikire"
  37,139,"Ndipo, ndithudi, Yona adali mmodzi wa Atumwi"
  37,140,Pamene iye adathawa kupita ku chombo chodzadza kwambiri ndi katundu
  37,141,Iye adachita nawo mayere koma iye adali mmodzi wa olephera
  37,142,Ndipo nsomba idamumeza iye chifukwa adalakwa
  37,143,Koma kukadakhala kuti sadapemphe chikhululukiro cha Mulungu wolemekezeka
  37,144,Ndithudi iye akadakhalabe m’mimba mwa nsomba mpaka tsiku la kuuka kwa akufa